|GKB-- Moonwell Draught ------------------------------------------|000

Current: |CKBChosen when cast|000
Command: |CKBmoonwell <current>|000
Guild Level: 27

Moonwell Draught binds one current of nwyfre into three short-lived
draughts.  Each draught restores that current when you drink it.

The draughts are bound to the druid who made them, cannot be sold, and
fade after a short time.  This is the high-level Druid answer to long
hunting sessions: prepare with profession materials, then keep moving.

Use |CKBreagents search <item>|000 to check the needed profession
materials.  The exact materials depend on the current you name.

Example:

  |CKBmoonwell daloan|000
  |CKBdrink draught|000
